<a class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-all hover:underline" href="/about">About</a>
<a class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-all hover:underline" href="/contact">Contact</a>
